"Fake" ? 

What does a couple of incomplete albums have to do with being "fake"? If this torrent was in actuality a Justin Bieber discography, THEN such a comment would be justified.

Anyhow, I'm pretty sure the uploader wasn't deliberately trying to mislead anyone here. The issue is probably caused by the file names for album and live versions of certain songs being the same, resulting in studio tracks being overwritten by live versions and vice-versa. 

So yeah, not a well made torrent by any stretch of the imagination, but hardly anything to get your panties knotted over. There's plenty of other IM discography torrents available. :D
